Task4:

#collect two strings from user
#string1: python
#String2: java

output ===> jythonpava64hv
==
str1 = input("Enter the 1st string : ")
str2 = input("Enter the 2nd string : ")

output_str = str2[0] + str1[1:] + str1[0] + str2[1:] + str(len(str1)) + str(len(str2))  + str1[int(len(str1)/2)] + str2[int(len(str2)/2)]

print("The output string is :", output_str)

OUTPUT: Enter the 1st string : python
Enter the 2nd string : java
The output string is : jythonpava64hv
