Task5:

#Collect two strings from user
#string1: wikipedia
#string2: typescript

output: p  +  c   ===> ascii value of p + ascii value of c  ====>  198
(ord , chr)


str1 = input("Enter the 1st string : ")
str2 = input("Enter the 2nd string : ")

str1_char_asci = ord(str1[int(len(str1)/2)])
str2_char_asci = ord(str2[int(len(str2)/2)])

asci_total = str1_char_asci + str2_char_asci
print("the asci value of middle char is :",asci_total)

OUTPUT:
Enter the 1st string : wikipedia
Enter the 2nd string : typescript
211
the asci value of middle char is : 211

